Package clientSide.gui

Class BookingEditingScreenController

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.controllers.AbstractScreen
      • clientSide.gui.BookingScreenController
        • clientSide.gui.BookingEditingScreenController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Stateful
    public class BookingEditingScreenController
extends BookingScreenController
    The BookingEditingScreenController is called after the visitor chose a reservation to edit/cancel from the table view in the BookingViewScreenController. In this screen, the visitor can modify his reservation, check park availability and cancel his reservation.
